Global 25kW DC AC Bidirectional Module Market Insights
25kW DC AC Bidirectional Module Market size was valued at USD 1.2 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 2.8 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 12.6% from 2024 to 2030.

25kW DC AC Bidirectional Module Market Overview
The global 25kW DC AC bidirectional module market has seen significant growth over the past few years, primarily driven by the increasing demand for energy-efficient and sustainable power solutions. As the energy sector moves towards renewable energy adoption, the need for advanced power electronics solutions, like the 25kW DC AC bidirectional module, is growing rapidly. This market was valued at approximately USD 1.5 billion in 2024 and is projected to reach around USD 3.2 billion by 2030, with a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 14% during the forecast period. The module’s ability to facilitate both energy storage and efficient energy exchange positions it as a vital component in the shift towards cleaner energy technologies. Additionally, the module’s ability to optimize energy usage within microgrids and electric vehicle (EV) applications further strengthens its market presence.

